nged\n1. `worker/src/index.ts` – Fixed sender email domain\n2. `app/(tabs)/(home)/index.tsx` – Fixed Arabic greeting text composition\n3. `expo/app/(tabs)/(home)/index.tsx` – Same fix synced\n4. `app/register.tsx` – Improved OTP error handling with localized messages\n5. `expo/app/register.tsx` – Same fix synced\n6. `expo/i18n/translations.ts` – Added missing translation keys\n\n---\n\n## Remaining: Worker Deployment\nThe previous Cloudflare API token has expired. **Please provide a fresh Cloudflare API token** so I can:\n1. Deploy the updated worker with the corrected sender domain\n2. Test the OTP endpoints live\n3. Confirm emails are actually being sent",
